graphics, video content','This foundational course introduces the critical concepts of Water, Sanitation, and Hygiene (WASH) and their role in promoting public health and well-being. Learn about global WASH challenges and solutions.','http://localhost:8080/uploads/courses/about-water-cernitation-and-hygine.jpg',1,'about-wash',4.50,'[\"Understand WASH fundamentals\",\"Learn about global WASH challenges\",\"Explore WASH solutions and interventions\",\"Apply WASH principles in communities\"]',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u4k2XY-fJJY',NULL,'english','2025-12-27 17:29:10','2025-12-27 17:29:10',NULL),('720e3a5c-793f-4b48-8d46-2dfb164fad2d',1,1,NULL,'Learning Water, Sanitation and Hygiene','Advanced training in WASH program implementation and community engagement strategies.',1,'advanced',15000.00,1,12000.00,'6 weeks','Implementation frameworks, assessment tools, evaluation templates','This advanced course provides in-depth training on implementing WASH programs, engaging communities, and ensuring sustainable water and sanitation solutions. Includes real-world case studies and practical exercises.','http://localhost:8080/uploads/courses/learning-water-sernitation-and-hygine.jpg',1,'learning-wash',4.80,'[\"Master WASH program implementation\",\"Develop community engagement strategies\",\"Conduct WASH assessments and evaluations\",\"Ensure program sustainability and impact\"]',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u4k2XY-fJJY',NULL,'english','2025-12-27 17:29:10','2025-12-27 17:29:10',NULL),('8ab77b6f-a6e0-46a7-ab69-d4c0bed82d2d',1,1,NULL,'Water and Sanitation Programs','Learn how to design and implement effective Water and Sanitation programs in communities.',1,'intermediate',20000.00,1,15000.00,'8 weeks','Project templates, implementation guides, monitoring tools','This practical course covers the design, implementation, and monitoring of water and sanitation programs in various contexts. Includes case studies and best practices from successful projects worldwide.','http://localhost:8080/uploads/courses/water-and-sanitation-program.jpg',1,'water-and-sanitation-programs',4.70,'[\"Design effective water and sanitation programs\",\"Implement community-based solutions\",\"Monitor and evaluate programs\",\"Ensure long-term sustainability\"]',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u4k2XY-fJJY',NULL,'english','2025-12-27 17:29:10','2025-12-27 17:29:10',NULL),('f0ebe495-0454-4574-bb66-161a54b65a4e',1,1,NULL,'Introduction to Water Treatment','Learn the fundamentals of water treatment processes including coagulation, flocculation, and sedimentation.',1,'beginner',0.00,0,0.00,'4 weeks','PDF guides, video tutorials, practice exercises','This comprehensive course covers the essential water treatment processes used in modern water treatment facilities. You will learn about coagulation, flocculation, sedimentation, and filtration techniques.','http://localhost:8080/uploads/courses/introduction-to-water-tratment.jpg',1,'introduction-to-water-treatment',4.50,'[\"Understand basic water treatment principles\",\"Learn coagulation and flocculation processes\",\"Master sedimentation techniques\",\"Apply filtration methods\"]',NULL,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u4k2XY-fJJY',NULL,'english','2025-12-27 17:29:10','2025-12-27 17:29:10',NULL);
